metadata.name: Deadpan
metadata.description:
Deadpan is a way of behaving that is expressionless or unemotional. But strong emotions and ideologies lurks beneath the surface. 

This artwork explores the theme of emotion suppression by employing a variety of expressions in various psychologically stimulating colors. 

Various society and cultural pressures can often lead people to suppress their emotions, in order to appear unaffected. 

Inspired by social fatigue and repetitive communication. 

3D and digital painting, deconstructed in AI using custom trained models
